Incident#1
The copyrighted work at issue is the article "Additional Discounts on Discount Office Furniture" by Erin Jones posted on the Article Insider web site at http://officeequipment.articleinsider.com/173632_discount_office_furniture.html
Search Query: "In addition to non-profits, school, churches, and military organizations also typically qualify for additional office supply discounts." Infringing Web Pages: http://www.your-office-furniture
